{"tid":2263350,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"【新手】集思廣益 養新貓困籠問題","createTime":"2020-10-29T23:22:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T11:22:44.000Z","uid":378026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f5b82cd30f6ca1f7a9c5e5d9aeeb2d9bd80c4171","tid":2263350,"uid":378026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T23:22:48.000Z","msg":"義工叫我困2個星期 但間唔中可以抱佢出黎<br />\n話怕貓貓係屋企會搗亂 跳上櫃頂再飛落黎<br />\n好多朋友都話唔困籠 困幾日就放佢自由出入<br />\n依家貓貓就好八卦 <br />\n有次換水唔記得關門 佢自己就走咗出黎 <br />\n但都係戰戰兢兢咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋屋企動靜大少少佢就縮<br />\n不過都嗲人嘅<br />\n同埋啲屎真係好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有一晚放佢出黎放電 第二日起身即刻係度叫<br />\n好似想出黎玩咁<br />\n所以我要唔要繼續放佢出黎 自出自入<br />\n定係平日放佢出黎放完電就擺翻佢入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求求各位巴絲比啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71665568c54a9e16f5209f47f041c79aee4caf68","tid":2263350,"uid":10453,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T23:27:28.000Z","msg":"只有一隻貓，裝晒窗網，出入大門小心走貓<br />\n<br />\n滿足以上條件可放，當佢透明就得"},{"pid":"cc953ee4e6fee9bd4538a2c12957b5e72c458cd6","tid":2263350,"uid":69178,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T23:31:23.000Z","msg":"執好多d野放房囉<br />\n我隻第3，4日已經放佢上床訓<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d933f58d662662cc4e937bbfc9dbad6d1c59e4","tid":2263350,"uid":2140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T23:32:05.000Z","msg":"冇困過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac35f327e0b9ca6ae70d3010db37f51b6f372bb0","tid":2263350,"uid":30837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T23:34:52.000Z","msg":"梗係唔困<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa9fb914df688704bffb57b2e3ce2734f65bc0ac","tid":2263350,"uid":378026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T23:59:40.000Z","msg":"咁其實點解義工話要困咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n貓貓3-4個月 個籠都係啱啱好夠位<br />\n真心想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c063d0a2066978570fc6c6999ad6adc93aed5413","tid":2263350,"uid":119146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T01:47:11.000Z","msg":"可能怕佢去到新環境唔習慣會病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想困籠咪放佢喺房先<br />\n慢慢加大個範圍<br />\n記得封好啲窿窿罅罅同收埋啲濕碎野"},{"pid":"de478659390acae08fa3aefe7469a1e4a92a7e6c","tid":2263350,"uid":110815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:01:03.000Z","msg":"我果隻衰仔 第一日返屋企已經唔肯入籠<br />\n一入籠就悲鳴 一放就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔驚人 從此我個籠就得個擺字<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得係睇佢性格嘅 你得佢一隻 又裝齊貓窗都可以試下放佢出黎嘅"},{"pid":"0a6d313485bfc1afa2e40e0f231e90bbdaa11270","tid":2263350,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T17:23:49.000Z","msg":"大籠？ 4 層"},{"pid":"23ecb90d638b58328d8f37d053b29f6e4afc6a3c","tid":2263350,"uid":141782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T19:01:02.000Z","msg":"我隻貓平時唔困<br />\n不過夜晚訓覺成日搞9我<br />\n我買咗個成張床咁大嘅籠for 佢夜晚訓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba114fdda025e95bdebd5e9578d3091af48c2d3f","tid":2263350,"uid":11382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T00:31:58.000Z","msg":"我隻貓都係岩岩返屋企一星期左右<br />\n見佢肯食野訓教就諗住開籠同佢玩下<br />\n一朝早就見佢去左窗邊望出面（落地玻璃）<br />\n但我又怕佢會一路stay係個度唔走<br />\n因為佢而家仲會對我哈氣，我埋唔到佢身"},{"pid":"e1221b47f1e581995dfe33f82e78d17e8f8e7388","tid":2263350,"uid":378026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba114fdda025e95bdebd5e9578d3091af48c2d3f","tid":2263350,"uid":11382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T00:31:58.000Z","msg":"我隻貓都係岩岩返屋企一星期左右<br />\n見佢肯食野訓教就諗住開籠同佢玩下<br />\n一朝早就見佢去左窗邊望出面（落地玻璃）<br />\n但我又怕佢會一路stay係個度唔走<br />\n因為佢而家仲會對我哈氣，我埋唔到佢身"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T07:57:51.000Z","msg":"我個隻就出黎玩得好開心<br />\n係屋企衝黎衝去 不過就成日自己嚇自己<br />\n呢幾日都會放佢出黎玩一陣放下電咁////<br />\n領養之前仲抱到 會咕咕咕<br />\n翻到屋企之後抱唔到 會攬住我條頸同叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ae2e6fa434b6dabda85dab08f605c4d09aeb2b","tid":2263350,"uid":378026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a6d313485bfc1afa2e40e0f231e90bbdaa11270","tid":2263350,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T17:23:49.000Z","msg":"大籠？ 4 層"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T07:58:28.000Z","msg":"細籠....."},{"pid":"1525b85173ca19e4a0a05fa394f9ac70fe8a9c0a","tid":2263350,"uid":378026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23ecb90d638b58328d8f37d053b29f6e4afc6a3c","tid":2263350,"uid":141782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T19:01:02.000Z","msg":"我隻貓平時唔困<br />\n不過夜晚訓覺成日搞9我<br />\n我買咗個成張床咁大嘅籠for 佢夜晚訓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T07:58:58.000Z","msg":"土地問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4baf50675c2c2989434e71e93a1497523d527e53","tid":2263350,"uid":378026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de478659390acae08fa3aefe7469a1e4a92a7e6c","tid":2263350,"uid":110815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:01:03.000Z","msg":"我果隻衰仔 第一日返屋企已經唔肯入籠<br />\n一入籠就悲鳴 一放就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔驚人 從此我個籠就得個擺字<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得係睇佢性格嘅 你得佢一隻 又裝齊貓窗都可以試下放佢出黎嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T07:59:37.000Z","msg":"放佢出黎都已經想搞破壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6218e2f2102211069097dad95f60f057f406d8","tid":2263350,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6ae2e6fa434b6dabda85dab08f6